Name: Start Date
Description: Start date for crash creation (i.e. mm/dd/yyyy)

Name: End Date
Description: Start date for crash creation (i.e. mm/dd/yyyy)

Name: Program Crash Minimum
Description: Minimum number of program crashes per day (i.e. 2)

Name: Program Crash Maximum
Description: Maximum number of program crashes per day (i.e. 5)

Name: Exclude Weekends
Description: Exclude weekends from generating crashes (TRUE or FALSE)

Name: Scatter Percentage
Description: Percentage of time to randomly skip crashes

Name: Start Hour
Description: The hour to start generating crashes
